        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1760529662" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15253452622417247157"><br/><br/><a href='http://vancouversun.com/entertainment/books/shoeless-joe-author-w-p-kinsella-has-died' rel='nofollow noopener'>Writer W.P. Kinsella did things his way. In failing health, he chose to end his life early Friday afternoon.</a><br/><br/>“W.P. (Bill) Kinsella invoked the assisted dying provisions of Bill C-14, at Hope, B.C., and passed away at 12:05 p.m. … Friday, Sept. 16, 2016,” said a statement from his agent, Carolyn Swayze.</span>
  <span id="freeText15253452622417247157" style="display:none"><br /><br /><a href="http://vancouversun.com/entertainment/books/shoeless-joe-author-w-p-kinsella-has-died" rel="nofollow noopener">Writer W.P. Kinsella did things his way. In failing health, he chose to end his life early Friday afternoon.</a><br /><br />“W.P. (Bill) Kinsella invoked the assisted dying provisions of Bill C-14, at Hope, B.C., and passed away at 12:05 p.m. … Friday, Sept. 16, 2016,” said a statement from his agent, Carolyn Swayze.</span>
