<span id="freeTextContainer16396138860544098050">I am not a baseball person by any means, despite Cooperstown being 45 minutes away. Maybe that is why I did not love this book. Maybe it&apos;s because I&apos;m a curmidgeonly young person who hates those tourists who find it in their best interest to do 30 MPH in a 45 MPH, and the main character Ray, reminded me of those tourists. <br/><a href='http://www.goodbooksandgoodwine.com/2009/07/shoeless-joe-by-w-p-kinsella.html' rel='nofollow noopener'>Read the rest of my review here</a></span>
